## Delete Question [/deletequestion/{id}]

As the user clicks on delete question button, it deletes the question from the database

### Delete a Question [DELETE]

+ Response 200

## Generating Quiz [/generatequiz/{cId}/{dId}]

Admin is able to generate a quiz which picks up the questions randomly from the question bank
based on the category Id and User Id

